# Student Management System in C

This repository contains a simple Student Management System program written in C language.

## Description
This program is used to store and display student details.
The user can enter student ID, name, and marks.
The program will display the entered details.

## Features
- Add student details
- Display student details
- Simple structure program
- Easy to understand

